{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549380/extras/TheFirstRogueBuilder_Banner.png?t=1738245880\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549380/extras/SteamDesc_Gif_TutoUSP_iteration_1.gif?t=1738245880\" /><br><br>Sick of other rogue-lites where random generation feels like a joke? Well, welcome to Cryptical Path, where the tables are turned! Forget the capricious whims of procedural dungeons, here, you are the master Architect.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549380/extras/ChooseYourOwnPath_Banner.png?t=1738245880\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549380/extras/KeyFeatures_2_iteration_1.gif?t=1738245880\" /><br><br>Cryptical Path is not just another rogue-lite, it allows you to build the rooms you want and manipulate the dungeon you are in. It is the first roguelite-builder, where you can express your creativity through thousands of possibilities. Forge your path through meticulously chosen rooms, sculpting an adventure that reflects your distinctive style and strategy!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549380/extras/ChooseYourOwnPath_Banner__1_.png?t=1738245880\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549380/extras/FightYourWayOut_iteration_1__1_.gif?t=1738245880\" /><br><br>Take back control of the ominous depths of the Hexium, a prison forged by your own hands to confine malevolent souls. Unravel the mysteries of your creation and navigate treacherous landscape, where every shadow conceals a potential threat, and every step forward brings you closer to the wrath of those you have condemned to an eternity of darkness.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549380/extras/KeyFeature_Banner.png?t=1738245880\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549380/extras/KeyFeatures_iteration_1.gif?t=1738245880\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Roguelite-builder: The ability to carve your dungeon, increasing the replayability and the control you have in each and every run.<br></li><li>Immersive world: Explore a beautifully crafter 3D side-scroller.<br></li><li>Fast paced action: Embody the Architect, a dynamic character that can dodge, dash and slash in the blink of an eye!<br></li><li>Constant progress: Unlock powerful items and choose which talents to master.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Trey the Scarecrow","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2549380/00b0d8503525a1715dc119e67f24872be0f43deb.jpg"},{"name":"Lady Ovenwoe - Act I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2549380/bf61f7a83d58b88f8a44720f7eda15453750e1e5.jpg"},{"name":"Lord Bookworm - Act II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2549380/28fca0f8d925715308a1822f2b93d20027a74b99.jpg"},{"name":"Doppelg\u00e4nger - Act III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2549380/8eae1754781f8ad618d04ca8a30161cdd014c284.jpg"},{"name":"1000?!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2549380/03f00725f6d92f65a3258711d9eb12b9d244e77c.jpg"},{"name":"I Am In Control","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2549380/5cc8744e8d15750e47427ab731a12d7f13205c59.jpg"},{"name":"Bol-Love-Aro","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2549380/0c4ac67048bea08589b7cc98b1264228551e9cd5.jpg"},{"name":"Object Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/254